snippet.title: Comic Book Nostalgia
snippet.description: Welcome to Comic Book Nostalgia, I'm C.B. Nostalgia and glad to see you here. This is your place for Marvel, DC and Independent comics in  Movies, TV, and print. We're here to provide opinions, news, trailer reactions, and reviews for your favorite superhero media. Join us for the best in MCU News, DC FIlms Scoops, and Streaming Goodness from around the globe! Excelsior!
